profile:
Georgian Bay Roofing provides durable, dependable roof repair and replacement services for home owners throughout the Tay, Tiny and Simcoe Township.
Our focus is on protecting your home, your possessions and your family from the sun, rain, wind, snow, and ice that are all part of our climate. We will focus on the entire roof system of your home, including the deck, ventilation, flashing, eavestrough and skylights.
Georgian Bay Roofing, division of M P Roofing Inc.
